# RegChain (regchain-fs)

Governance wrapper for regulated AI workflows: policy controls, audit trail, evaluation harness, and validation memo artifacts.

## Install (dev + credit demo)
```bash
python -m venv .venv
.venv\Scripts\activate
pip install -U pip
pip install -e ".[dev,credit]"
